- Do not translate Devanagari terms to English in subject/object fields.
- Use type="practice" for farm operations (e.g., जीवामृत बनवणे, बीजामृत उपचार).
- Use type="observation" for seasonal/weather patterns described in the text.
- Use type="prescription" for "if X then apply Y" recommendations with quantities.

